        "product_description": {
            "value": "ParaLace 550 Paracord Shoelaces are built for adventure and designed to withstand the most rugged outdoor environments. Made from durable 550 paracord and sold in pairs, these round hiking boot laces are highly resistant to abrasion, weather, wear and tear, and UV deterioration. With a 550lb static load strength and low-stretch nylon construction, your knots hold in place for fewer adjustments and more comfortable movement. Featuring a kernmantle design of 9 removable inner nylon strands enclosed in a woven nylon sheath and capped with 4mm black metal aglets, these laces fit most hiking boots, running shoes, work boots, and combat boots. They also double as versatile survival gear: build a snare, make a sling, extract fishing line, hang a hammock, secure a shelter and more. Available in 48, 54, 60, 72, and 81 inch lengths.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
